					<p>I really love this. Its one of my favourites of yours. It begins beautifully &#8211; really like the alliteration.</p>
<p>I only found it slightly sad. For me it was mostly magical (like &#8216;the indian in the cupboard&#8217; kind of magic one finds in everyday life and things). I loved the descriptions of the two families &#8211; they were so rich and evocative.</p>
